msgstr "[LINK:data/help/menu_military]Caratteristiche militari[/LINK]"

#: menus:112
msgid "[C:7:0:1]Command Squads[C:7:0:0]"
msgstr "[C:7:0:1]Comanda squadre[C:7:0:0]"

#: menus:109
msgid ""
"Press [IKEY:D_SQUADS] to order your squads to station at a new location or "
"to send them on patrols."
